162
00:10:15,660 --> 00:10:16,830
Baiklah.

163
00:10:17,490 --> 00:10:18,950
Pak Kim.

164
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,250
<i>Ada apa?</i>

165
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:29,130
Grid sudah rusak dua kali...

166
00:10:29,210 --> 00:10:30,720
